               <p>RICHARD MOSELEY. I live at Mr. Coates', <placeName id="t18270531-131-crimeloc679">George-street, Bethnal-green</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18270531-131-crimeloc679" type="placeName" value="George-street, Bethnal-green"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18270531-131-crimeloc679" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270531-131-off677 t18270531-131-crimeloc679"></join> - the prisoner lodged in the same room, and generally got up before me. On the 12th of April, when I got up, he was gone; a man who slept with me missed his watch; I then missed my boots, and next day, (which was Good Friday,) the other things from a box, of which I had lost the key, and taken the lock off.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270531-131-person814">
                  STEPHEN 
                  HUTLEY
               <interp inst="t18270531-131-person814" type="surname" value="HUTLEY"></interp>
