                     <interp inst="t18270531-131-person814" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am son-in-law of Mr. Coates. - On Good Friday evening, between eight and nine o'clock, I found the prisoner at the Crown and Anchor public-house, Somer's-town, with Moseley's clothes on - he has a wife and child I understand.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270531-131-person815">
